The paper discusses the development of a deep learning-based framework for conducting stealthy attacks in industrial control systems, which involves intrusion detection, anomaly detection, and cyber-physical systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
